-   A task can be immediately inserted into a DSQ from ``ops.select_cpu()``
-   by calling ``scx_bpf_dsq_insert()``. If the task is inserted into
-   ``SCX_DSQ_LOCAL`` from ``ops.select_cpu()``, it will be inserted into the
